<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-6">Food and amenities on-site</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="no">Cafe<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Patient library <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="not-answered">Pharmacy <span>(not answered)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Shop<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
