<div id="imageContent1fe163e3beb44acba71a1e63ea7a6585">
</div>
<p>Disabled parking spaces are conveniently located near to the front entrance. There is flat disabled access directly into the main entrance and all outpatient departments are situated on the ground floor. Wheelchairs are available on arrival. The ward and theatre departments are located on the first floor with both lift and stair access. </p>
